Siya Kolisi's wife Rachel has recounted how her husband's car was broken into. Rachel shared the information on her Instagram Stories that her husband's car was broken into but fortunately a car guard managed to catch the criminal. “Siya's car was broken into two hours ago. The car guard caught the guy. We called the cops and still waiting for them to arrive. Also, don't ever bother calling 10111 ever. They literally don't answer the phone.”